features.text:
Crypto-Frens is a non-generative, handcrafted 1/1 collection of 100 Frens by artist Sascha Salender.

Each Fren is unique in its appearance and has its own traits.

Crypto Frens are multi-value-NFTs. You get the Fren pfp Image and the original vox file, so you can use your Fren as an avatar for the metaverse. The NFT image is 3000x3000 pixel, so you can make your Fren a real-life artwork (By printing it to a medium or whatever comes to your mind) which you can hang in your Fren-cave.

Crypto Junkies is a handcrafted Limited NFT Collection created by artist Sascha Salender.

Every crypto junkie is unique and inspired by the deep needs and addictions of modern day people - creeping around to consume any NFT they get their hands on. The Junkies are pursuing a place they can call home in the Metaverse. But land ain't cheap. And so they sell themselves to help their creator become a landlord and give them a place to find peace, create art and do good.

This is me (drknss.eth)
I'm also a CRYPTO JUNKIE. You can find me at 2nd Floor

features.text:
Frens are here to connect with each other and build a strong community. Frens think that roadmaps kill the fun, so they want you to take part in the community and come up with ideas, where the journey will take us.

Will it be a colaboration parcel for all holders on Cryptovoxels? A merch collection? Illustrated comics? A graphic novel? Animated shorts? Art airdrops? You'll never know if you don't join the discord.

To fulfil this goal they want to give 30% of the total earnings to UNICEF, helping street children all over the world.

Once land is bought there will be ongoing NFT drops and exhibitions to support different charity goals and spread the art of drknss.

You can use your Crypto Junkie as a profile picture or as an avatar in the Metaverse - the NFT holds the original vox file.
The builds you can see here are made by me. You can hire me for parcel building and custom voxel creations. Feel free to DM me on twitter in case you need help
